=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係NDS大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa1925e803a4ddfb28efd6cadf3e5032926e244","tid":617550,"uid":132227,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T19:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>把口就講反中港融合<br />\n實際上玩淘寶、放假過深圳玩<br />\n仲越黎越多人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>兩個問題<br />\n1. 幫襯淘寶,去深圳玩=中港融合?<br />\n去日本玩=日港融合?<br />\n<br />\n2. 我唔知你身邊群咩人, 我身邊就冇人去深圳玩<br />\n去東莞融合結合就聽得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1. 唔想中港融合係咪會唔鍾意中國<br />\n咁唔鍾意一個國家係咪應該抵制佢？<br />\n用淘寶、放假就去深圳玩只會增加對中國既好感<br />\n從而令到反中港融合更加冇說服力<br />\n中國人保釣都會抵制日貨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 大學生<br />\n<br />\n請繼續出招</blockquote>1. 其實你到底知唔知咩叫中港融合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔好逼我地變到跟佢地個套<br />\n同埋唔好死咁多人落黎搞亂我地呢套<br />\n佢地要點衰我唔care<br />\n買野只係生意往來<br />\n完左就係咁先<br />\n唔會有任何感情<br />\n<br />\n2. band 3雞校生你當左大學生咋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係NDS大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1. 用淘寶+睇大陸節目-&gt;同大陸人生活模式開始相似<br />\n番深圳玩-&gt;如果係對中國咁反感點會去？<br />\n依啲嘢潛移默化下會令香港開始相似大陸<br />\n加上而家中國做既嘢香港都只係食下花生0行動<br />\n咁點樣唔「搞亂自己嗰套」？<br />\n2. 唔好將自己嗰套放落我到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你自己圈子層次咁低就神化大學生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea736bb14959d0a63b539f1adb4ea3fe722f1b6f","tid":617550,"uid":73310,"like":9,"disl