on買野就同美國人生活模式相似？<br />\n上Rakuten買野就同日本人生活模式相似？<br />\n咁新移民上HKTV買野係咪代佢地同香港人生活模式相似？<br />\n定你以為網上購物係由支那人發明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你話多人番深圳玩姐 <br />\n咁可能物以類聚<br />\n你身邊多人番深圳玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲雙非中學生的確幾鍾意大陸節目<br />\n但你當個啲連廣東話未必識嘅人係香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 咁我認我層次底入唔到三大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我圈子啲低層次同學都冇你所講嘅鍾意去深圳/支那地方玩啵<br />\n咁你呢啲高層次人又係邊到識到邊啲大學生鍾意去深圳玩呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/090652_c24de70b68744028aa45cb7212255827.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F090652_c24de70b68744028aa45cb7212255827.png&h=5bbae068&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7cae4e5de70410c1a17f3102cece0f3d357ed71","tid":617550,"uid":132227,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 網上購物=同大陸人生活模式相似？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上Amazon買野就同美國人生活模式相似？<br />\n上Rakuten買野就同日本人生活模式相似？<br />\n咁新移民上HKTV買野係咪代佢地同香港人生活模式相似？<br />\n定你以為網上購物係由支那人發明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你話多人番深圳玩姐 <br />\n咁可能物以類聚<br />\n你身邊多人番深圳玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲雙非中學生的確幾鍾意大陸節目<br />\n但你當個啲連廣東話未必識嘅人係香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 咁我認我層次底入唔到三大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我圈子啲低層次同學都冇你所講嘅鍾意去深圳/支那地方玩啵<br />\n咁你呢啲高層次人又係邊到識到邊啲大學生鍾意去深圳玩呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/090652_c24de70b68744028aa45cb7212255827.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F090652_c24de70b68744028aa45cb7212255827.png&h=5bbae068&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n1. 我冇講過網上購物=同大陸人似<br />\n只係覺得對一個地方咁反感<br />\n而且咁反對中港融合既時候<br />\n點解仲要用咁多淘寶 建立咁多文化同生意交流？<br />\n<br />\n我成個post係講緊有好多香港人係咁<br />\n開facebook youtube望下都有好多KOL番深圳<br />\n依件事唔紅就唔會拍咁多番深圳玩既片啦<br />\n<br />\n你唔肯接受現實就算 事實係我有朋友連去到外國讀書都要睇大陸劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 識多啲人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我去叫朋友借張學生證比我遮名寫id <br />\n我咩u都係添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a995d711422da170958bfce88e0c16292cecfb","tid":617550,"uid":60070,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4767091b5b82b2c05778079f8b8da2d42f1caeb2","tid":617550,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:05:24.000Z","msg":"把口就講反中港融合<br />\n實際上玩淘寶、放假過深圳玩<br />\n仲越黎越多人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T05:05:13.000Z","msg":"覺得連登仔精神分裂得好嚴重<br />\n<br />\n把口就講反中港融合<br />\n實際上玩淘寶、放假過深圳玩<br />\n仲越黎越多人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上得多連登以為全香港人都反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32fa18e693d0b9f90f282307f088a166d4c165b","tid":617550,"uid":73310,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a7cae4e5de70410c1a17f3102cece0f3d357ed71","tid":617550,"uid":132227,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 網上購物=同大陸人生活模式相似？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上Amazon買野就同美國人生活模式相似？<br />\n上Rakuten買野就同日本人生活模式相似？<br />\n咁新移民上HKTV買野係咪代佢地同香港人生活模式相似？<br />\n定你以為網上購物係由支那人發明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你話多人番深圳玩姐 <br />\n咁可能物以類聚<br />\n你身邊多人番深圳玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲雙非中學生的確幾鍾意大陸節目<br />\n但你當個啲連廣東話未必識嘅人係香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 咁我認我層次底入唔到三大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我圈子啲低層次同學都冇你所講嘅鍾意去深圳/支那地方玩啵<br />\n咁你呢啲高層次人又係邊到識到邊啲大學生鍾意去深圳玩呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/090652_c24de70b68744028aa45cb7212255827.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F090652_c24de70b68744028aa45cb7212255827.png&h=5bbae068&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n1. 我冇講過網上購物=同大陸人似<br />\n只係覺得對一個地方咁反感<br />\n而且咁反對中港融合既時候<br />\n點解仲要用咁多淘寶 建立咁多文化同生意交流？<br />\n<br />\n我成個post係講緊有好多香港人係咁<br />\n開facebook youtube望下都有好多KOL番深圳<br />\n依件事唔紅就唔會拍咁多番深圳玩既片啦<br />\n<br />\n你唔肯接受現實就算 事實係我有朋友連去到外國讀書都要睇大陸劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 識多啲人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我去叫朋友借張學生證比我遮名寫id <br />\n我咩u都係添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T05:34:27.000Z","msg":"1. 你自己係#15話用淘寶-&gt; 同大陸人生活模式開始相似<br />\n淘寶呢個方式咪=網上購物<br />\n咁點樣冇講過網上購物=同大陸人生活模式似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買下mon貼就叫文化交流？<br />\n你搞清楚咩叫中港融合<br />\n點為之反對中港融合先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 邊似得你識得咁多鍾意支那野嘅人姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唯有神化下圈子內嘅人嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你識咁多大學生，咪咩U嘅學生證都貼幾張上黎囉<br />\n都係個句，物以類聚啦高層次人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3ed8b892af1f009700bc21b13fdc466ab83c73","tid":617550,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T05:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/134116_46a7eeace4bc797ce8450b3c886b80a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F134116_46a7eeace4bc797ce8450b3c886b80a1.png&h=6850bdf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本香港最不知所謂既就係八十後<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/614054/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/614054/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">之前屌八十後條撚樣咪係囉<br />\n佢話自己心繫香港架</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608bea8b5fdab4be1dc8d0983b03795184c7af05","tid":617550,"uid":132227,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:12:43.000Z","msg":"quote]1. 你自己係#15話用淘寶-&gt; 同大陸人生活模式開始相似<br />